  {
    "hotel_id": "1179186",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/atlas-hoi-an-hotel_3/hotel/hoi-an-vn.html",
    "name": "Mulberry Collection Silk Eco",
    "detail": "This is a new hotel in Hoi An. Close to town (5 mins walk) and they provide free bicycle to use (although I took the motorcycle across the hotel). When I checked in, they were professional and had detailed explanation of the hotel with welcome drink. The hotel room was clean, new and nicely design. It is modern and spacious toilet. They have Wifi and good amenities. Breakfast was good but on the second day, due to low level of customers, they had ala carte style. They do have gym and spa although I didn't had time to visit them. The pool is great to chill out. The taxi transfer is more expensive but if you would like convenience, that will do. Outside the hotel, they have F&B stalls and local food. During check out, I had a late flight out, so I lingered by the pool, have a cool dip and rinse at their shower area. They allowed me to use their towel and their toilet to change. Overall, they were accommodating and friendly staffs. ",
